Green Iron Summary
Creation:
Magic Block of Conversion converts Iron Ingots into Green Iron Ingots
Crafting:
Green Iron Ingots → Green Iron Blocks
Usage:
Green Iron Blocks → Green Iron Golem (friendly unless attacked, stronger than normal golems)
Green Iron Ingots → Upgrade Diamond Tools to Green Essence Tools via Smithing Table
Notes:
Part of the green material progression: Paper → Green Paper → Magic Block → Green Iron → Green Essence Tools
Provides late-game utility and tool progression
